Hello Rafealla,
Would you be able to meet me at your place at 8:30 tomorrow morning ?
We can have a site meeting together and discuss the next steps in our proce=
ss and answer any questions which you may have at this point.
Please let me know if this is workable for you.
Regards,
Grant.

