<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-bottom:12.0pt">On 27 Aug 2025, at 4:=
30<span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif">=E2=80=AF</span>=
PM, Grant Metson &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Mets=
on@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:<o:p></o:p></p>
</blockquote>
