<blockquote style=3D"margin-top:5.0pt;margin-bottom:5.0pt">
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-s=
erif">=EF=BB=BF</span> <o:p>
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi Rafaella,</span>=
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I can give you a mo=
re comprehensive update on Friday. But for now =E2=80=93 I can briefly resp=
ond as below:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your Claims manager=
 will update you on the content=E2=80=99s aspect of your claim. I have no k=
nowledge or jurisdiction on the contents claim. However, I will follow up w=
ith your claims manager for that contents side
 of things on Friday when I=E2=80=99m back in the office.</span><o:p></o:p>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re =E2=80=93 your o=
wn assessment =E2=80=93 you are welcome to book that in very soon. I would =
recommend that we meet again at your home early next week before you do tha=
t. It would be very beneficial to meet onsite again
 and have a face-to-face update on the claim=E2=80=99s progression.</span><=
o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As you know we have=
 inspected the exterior wall cavities and have found some smoke contaminati=
on in some isolated areas =E2=80=93 so we will explore that further to ensu=
re that it is included in the scope of work.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I=E2=80=99m travell=
ing all day tomorrow =E2=80=93 but will endeavor to provide you with a more=
 comprehensive update on Friday.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please let me know =
if you would like to book a site meeting in for next week.</span><o:p></o:p=
></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regards,</span><o:p=
></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant. </span><o:p>=
</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span><o:p><=
/o:p></p>
